'''飓风黛比'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Debby}}）是[[1982年大西洋飓风季|1982年大西洋飓风季]]最强烈的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是该季第四场获得命名的风暴和仅有的[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时215公里。系统于9月13日经向西移动的[[东风波|东风波]]在[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]北岸近海发展形成，成为热带低气压后向西北方向移动，再于次日增强成热带风暴并获名“黛比”。此后，风暴快速强化，于9月15日清晨升级成飓风，然后回转向东北方向前进，于次日以二级飓风强度掠过[[百慕大|百慕大]]。气旋继续增强，于9月18日短暂达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]升至每小时215公里，最低[[气压|气压]]950[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.05[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。

达到最高强度后，黛比缓慢减弱，于9月19日清晨以二级或一级飓风强度从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]以南经过。此后，风暴的移动速度大幅提高，以每小时95公里的速度向东前进。9月20日，气旋急速逼近[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]，并在不久后转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]受到的总体影响很小，[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]、[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]和[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]降下小到中雨。百慕大因狂风致使局部地区停电，另有部分树木倒塌，但全岛所受破坏程度很轻。此外，飓风还在纽芬兰岛产生降水和中等强度风力。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Debby 1982 track.png}}
9月3日，有扰动天气系统离开非洲海岸进入大西洋，其规模起初很小，并且不到24小时后就一度失去踪影。9月7日，卫星图像表明这股扰动天气发展出环流，但这些环流次日又已消失。残留的[[东风波|东风波]]继续移动，于9月11日进入[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]海域，气象机构派出侦察机前去观测。侦察机起初发现环流，但到了次日又只遗留下强劲的东风波。外界大气环境变得更有利于系统发展，[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]附近洋面的[[风切变|风切变]]连续数日都很少。气象部门在系统进入该岛海域期间再度派出侦察机，并根据观测结果宣布系统于9月13日在[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]近海发展成热带低气压。<ref name="TCRPage1">{{cite report | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Debby Preliminary Report (Page 1) | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221809/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>

接下来飞入气旋的侦察机发现中心气压降至1005[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.67[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），风速则提升至每小时70公里，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此于9月14日早上将其升级成热带风暴，并以“黛比”（{{lang|en|Debby}}）命名。不过，气象机构难以确定风暴接下来是会同逐渐逼近的低压槽相互影响，还是开始受到[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]上空的[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响。黛比之后受低压槽影响开始北上，逐渐远离陆地。经过强化，气旋于9月14日晚达到飓风强度下限。风暴接下来进一步增强，持续风速在逼近百慕大期间达到每小时180公里，成为二级飓风。9月16日，黛比从百慕大以西约130公里洋面经过并继续北上。<ref name="TCRPage1" />

[[File:Hurricane_Debby_1982_peak_intensity.jpg|thumb]]

9月17日，系统的移动速度减缓至每小时10公里，但进入[[西风带|西风带]]内部的低压槽后又大幅提升至每小时50公里<ref name="TCRPage1" />。在此期间，黛比达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]215公里，最低气压950毫巴（百帕，28.05英寸汞柱）的最高强度，成为四级飓风<ref name="TCRPage1" />。9月19日清晨，风暴从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）以南近海掠过，再于次日加速东进，前进速度达到每小时100公里<ref name="TCRPage2">{{cite report | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Debby Preliminary Report (Page 2) | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180913/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim02.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。穿越大西洋期间，黛比一直保有热带天气系统特征，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月20日降级成热带风暴，并于当天转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]后不久急速逼近[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]<ref name="TCRPage5">{{cite report | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Debby Preliminary Report (Page 5) | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim05.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303173855/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/debby/prelim05.gif | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | date =  }}</ref>。

黛比的残留行进至北欧上空时仍保有充足对流，于9月21日吹袭[[芬兰|芬兰]]北部，该国称其为风暴毛里<ref>{{cite news | title = Mauri-hirmumyrsky riehui Lapissa 1982 | archivedate = 2016-02-15 | deadurl = no | publisher = Yle | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160215230902/http://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2009/09/22/mauri-hirmumyrsky-riehui-lapissa-1982 | url = http://yle.fi/aihe/artikkeli/2009/09/22/mauri-hirmumyrsky-riehui-lapissa-1982 | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | date = 2009-09-22 }}</ref>，是有纪录以来袭击该国的最强风暴之一。时速超过137公里的狂风导致大量树木倒塌，倒塌树木的总体积高达数百万立方英里，[[凯米|凯米]]和[[托尔尼奥|托尔尼奥]]受到[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]重创，还有两人丧生。<ref name="Yle">{{cite web | year = 2012 | title = Is Finland hurricane-proof? | publisher = Yleisradio | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212820/http://yle.fi/uutiset/is_finland_hurricane-proof/6356639 | deadurl = no | url = http://yle.fi/uutiset/is_finland_hurricane-proof/6356639 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>

从1982年大西洋飓风季开始，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机开始根据[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]飓风研究部的指令执行向风暴投放[[投落送|投落送]]，这种设备可以极低频欧米茄信号，用于了解及估算投落送进入风暴某些特定位置之后的动向，黛比便是最早的实验风暴之一<ref name="P-3">{{cite web | author = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2007 | title = NOAA's Gulfstream-IV Jet Takes Hurricane Track Predictions to New Heights | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002326/http://celebrating200years.noaa.gov/transformations/aircraft/welcome.html#path | url = http://celebrating200years.noaa.gov/transformations/aircraft/welcome.html#path }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Debby_1982_rainfall.png|thumb]]
黛比在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]产生的降雨量从最北端的76毫米左右到最南侧的250毫米不等。岛上以[[佩纽埃拉斯|佩纽埃拉斯]]降水最多，达326毫米。[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]测得约76毫米雨量，[[多米尼加|多米尼加]]则达到130毫米。<ref name="HPC">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | date = 2007-06-20 | title = Incipient Stage of Debby - September 12–14, 1982 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091357/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/debby1982.html | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/debby1982.html | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>[[美国海军|美国海军]]将位于百慕大空军基地的700名工作人员转移到附近的体育馆。随着飓风逼近，数以千计的游客于9月16日搭乘最后的航班离开该岛。多家航空公司减少进出百慕大的航班数量。[[东方航空_(美国)|东方航空]]将原有的五班缩减至两班，只保留百慕大飞往[[纽约|纽约]]、[[纽华克_(新泽西州)|纽华克]]和[[波士顿|波士顿]]的班机。<ref name="Bermudaevac4">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 1982-09-16 | title = Debby passes Bermuda isles | publisher = The Courier | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xKIKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=qkwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6858,47468&dq=hurricane+debby+bermuda&hl=zh-CN | archive-date = 2022-03-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220323193116/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=xKIKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=qkwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6858%2C47468&dq=hurricane+debby+bermuda&hl=zh-CN }}</ref>

风暴在百慕大产生的持续风速高达每小时180公里，气象机构预测其风眼会于次日从该岛上空经过<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1982-09-16 | title = Crowds Flee Bermuda With Hurricane Near | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/16/world/crowds-flee-bermuda-with-hurricane-near.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160512215918/http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/16/world/crowds-flee-bermuda-with-hurricane-near.html | archivedate = 2016-05-12 }}</ref>。多家航空公司的班机取消，部分建筑以木板封死，邮轮则赶在飓风来袭前匆忙离港<ref>{{cite web | author = The Daily Intelligencer | date = 1982-09-16 | title = Hurricane Debby Gains Strength | publisher = The Daily Intelligencer}}</ref>。救援工作组将风暴沿途附近[[美孚石油|美孚石油]]钻井平台上的工作人员转移<ref>{{cite news | author = Syracuse Herald-Journal | date = 1982-09-19 | title = Newfoundland battered | publisher = Syracuse Herald-Journal}}</ref>。百慕大出现强烈阵风，虽有轻度破坏，但没有出现人员伤亡。岛上局部地区停电，但很快便已修复<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160317035631/http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/17/world/around-the-world-a-wandering-hurricane-brushes-past-bermuda.html | date = 1982-09-17 | title = A Wandering Hurricane Brushes Past Bermuda | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-17 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/17/world/around-the-world-a-wandering-hurricane-brushes-past-bermuda.html }}</ref>。岛上还有许多树木被狂风推倒<ref>{{cite web | agency = Associated Press | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 1982-09-18 | accessdate = 2012-01-01 | title = Hurricane Debby Heads North After Brushing by Bermuda | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304234218/http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/18/world/hurricane-debby-heads-north-after-brushing-by-bermuda.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | newspaper = The New York Times | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1982/09/18/world/hurricane-debby-heads-north-after-brushing-by-bermuda.html }}</ref>。

风暴逼近加拿大期间，纽芬兰岛近海多个石油钻井平台的工作人员撤离，正在[[纽芬兰大浅滩|纽芬兰大浅滩]]开展的科学实验也相应中止。受黛比影响，纽芬兰岛东南部降下小雨，最高降雨量约有89毫米。此外，还有少数区域出现热带风暴强度大风，但总体破坏程度很轻。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=2AFDDF8B-1 | title = 1982-Debby | date = 2010-09-14 | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-05-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212938/http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=2AFDDF8B-1 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>

